Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我是桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,唷 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在当地开演讲会 和赞助商喝到早上 现在才起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,听说因为台风新干线停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 现在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,仙台 似乎不会恢复运行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,同一辆新干线上 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是说宗谷先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 现在我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 你们在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,找到住处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是 仙台站附近的盛泉旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 既然和你在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,听不到呢
